    "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/decision/nagaraja-cou1-decision-001",
    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/fda-osel-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required credibility levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieves level 2 against a required level 3, which is accepted given the single-configuration scope of the COU and the availability of supplementary fatigue data outside this package. Overall credibility is judged sufficient for a Medium model risk, Medium decision consequence context. ValidationResults supporting the Output comparison factor were generated under ModelConfiguration 2024-q3-build-2; the UofA currentModelVersion is 2026-q1-build-7. The assessment team notes this version drift and considers it acceptable pending re-execution of validation runs under the current model build.",
